      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and usage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor paint fading, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and carpets. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, but a potential buyer should be prepared for upcoming routine maintenance as some components are nearing the end of their service life. It is a solid, functional option for someone looking for a dependable vehicle who doesn't mind some aesthetic imperfections.",
