    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a joy to drive and has always been super reliable for me! It\u2019s in really solid shape, has been well-maintained, and is totally ready to hit the road with its next owner. It\u2019s perfect if you\u2019re looking for something dependable that still looks and feels great without the brand-new price tag. Feel free to reach out\u2014I\u2019d love for you to come by, see it in person, and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
